unittitle_ssm: Records of the Office of the Associate Dean of the School of Education (Louis Kleinman)
abstract_ssm: The Records of the Office of the Associate Dean of the School of Education contain mostly correspondence and memoranda between various School department heads and faculty and the Office of the Associate Dean, usually represented either by Dr. Elliot Mininberg, or the Associate Dean himself, Dr. Louis Kleinman. The memoranda are frequently budgetary in nature, requesting money allocation for departmental needs. There are also a number of different School of Education publications representing the interests and goals of the School's various departments.
